dcterms:creator: J. Yang
J. Leskovec
dcterms:description: The Youtube dataset contains a social network of users, where each community is a ground-truth group on Youtube. Only node adjacency is available for this dataset.
dcterms:title: Youtube

dcterms:creator: J. McAuley
J. Leskovec
dcterms:description: The Amazon Co-Purchase dataset provides product categories as the ground-truth labels. It is a graph such that, if a product is 'also-bought' with another product at least three times, then there is an undirected edge between them. Each product is associated with the product title.
dcterms:title: Amazon Co-Purchase

dcterms:creator: H. Yin
A. R. Benson
J. Leskovec
D. F. Gleich
dcterms:description: The Wikipedia page-link dataset is a web graph of Wikipedia hyperlinks. In addition to the graph topology, every node is associated with the title of the wiki page. The page category is the ground-truth community label.
dcterms:title: Wikipedia Page-Link

dcterms:creator: J. Zhang
P. S. Yu
dcterms:description: The ArnetMiner coauthor dataset comes with co-author relations and affiliation, job, research keywords.
dcterms:title: ArnetMiner-LinkedIn

dcterms:creator: J. Zhang
P. S. Yu
dcterms:description: The DBLP co-author network contains a large number of nodes and edges representing academic publications and their authors.
dcterms:title: DBLP

dcterms:description: The Fliker-Last.fm dataset consists of two social networks, where the links represent friendships.
dcterms:title: Fliker-Last.fm

dcterms:description: The E-commerce Web Server Log dataset consists of server logs from an e-commerce website, capturing user interactions and requests.
